summary:
You can write about your years of experience, industry, or skills. People also talk about their achievements or previous job experiences.

Hi there, My name is Mohammad and im a: Team member Parts Trading/Aircraft Technician by KLM Royal Dutch Airlines/Private Pilot/ ATPL Student and the founder of Taalgericht BV. 
I fly for fun and hopefully I’ll achieve my dream by getting my ATPL. 
Social Positive team worker and enthusiastic,i could learn anything and i would love to know about almost everything so I’m really curious.
 I'm Open to new possibilities and I love to try new things.
